    <item>
      <title>波音、空客削减产量导致航空供应商高管离职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/aerospace-supplier-senior-plunges-as-boeing-airbus-cut-output</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国航空零部件供应商 Senior Plc 发出警告称，由于供应链问题和波音公司遭遇严重罢工，该公司对空中客车公司和波音公司的短期销售额将下降，随后其股价出现四年多来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/aerospace-supplier-senior-plunges-as-boeing-airbus-cut-output</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 07:35:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Vistry 股价在盈利预警后出现英国脱欧以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/vistry-shares-plunge-after-homebuilder-posts-profit-warning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[房屋建筑商 Vistry Group Plc 宣布调整后全年利润将比之前预测的低 8000 万英镑（1.05 亿美元），随后股价出现八年来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/vistry-shares-plunge-after-homebuilder-posts-profit-warning</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 07:24:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中欧关系恶化 中国调查欧盟汽车 并向白兰地征收关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/china-slaps-levy-on-european-brandy-amid-worsening-trade-ties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国正在研究提高大引擎汽车的关税，并将开始对来自欧洲的白兰地征收关税，这在欧盟决定对中国电动汽车征收关税后，加剧了贸易争端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/china-slaps-levy-on-european-brandy-amid-worsening-trade-ties</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 07:07:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
